Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: pylint-starlark
Version: 1.1
Summary: Run pylint on Starlark files.
Home-page: https://github.com/phgn0/pylint-starlark
Author: Peter Hagen
Author-email: peter@phgn.io
License: MIT
Download-URL: https://github.com/phgn0/pylint-starlark/archive/1.1.tar.gz
Description: 
        Use pylint for Starlark files, by doing an AST transform of load() calls into python import statements.
        
        Use it by running `pylint-starlark file.star`, which internally calls `pylint` with the `pylint-starlark-plugin` plugin enabled.
        You may also run it `via python3 -m pylint_starlark file.star`.
        
Keywords: pylint,starlark,plugin
